10 An Act relating to wildlife habitat development;
amending 29 O.S. 2021, Section 3-312, which relates
11 to a program to promote wildlife habitat development
on private lands; exempting land in the program from
12 eminent domain; allowing the Department of Wildlife
Conservation to establish certain program; requiring
13 projects to be completed at landowner’s expense;
exempting land in the program from eminent domain;
14 allowing for landowners to cancel contract; requiring
