19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
20 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 29 O.S. 2021, Section 3-312, is
21 amended to read as follows:
22 Section 3-312. A. In order to encourage wildlife habitat
23 conservation on private lands, the Department of Wildlife
24 Conservation shall establish a program for wildlife habitat
